Why did not the Pe- ruvians impart that reverence for God, and contempt for the evil spirit to the Abipones, at the same time that they instructed' them in a religious observance of the Pleiades? Because vice is more easily learnt than virtue, as healthy persons are sooner infected by the sick, than sick ones cured by the healthy.
